            "content": "<p><span class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"><a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@Snoro\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@<span>Snoro</span></a></span> </p><p>How much of this money is wasted on scams and schemes that do nothing but add to the problem of climate change? </p><p>Only 2 examples are listed in this article; <br>carbon capture (scam) and electric airplanes (part of the 'electrify everything!'  scam that adds to the climate crisis with more mining, more destruction of the planet and requiring more electrical infrastructure covering the planet).</p><p>In other words, BAU that caused the climate crisis to begin with. </p><p>The easiest and quickest solution is to slash our energy use worldwide, (the lockdown of 2020 showed us that) eliminating the needless energy users (there are tons of those) and cutting back on the most harmful/wasteful. </p><p>But that would cut into Corps profits. <br>\ud83d\ude44</p><p>Most intelligent species on the planet, my ass.</p>",
